(63, 6, 1, '', '2024-01-05 01:23:21', 674, 4786, '12e25a4d7176c0a4c11c40947bce298cda9f8dc4', '{\"id\":6,\"asset_id\":\"78\",\"title\":\"118 v\\u00f5 sinh Ki\\u00ean Giang thi th\\u0103ng \\u0111\\u1eb3ng Taekwondo\",\"alias\":\"118-vo-sinh-kien-giang-thi-thang-d-ng-taekwondo\",\"introtext\":\"<h2 class=\\\"title-italic\\\">(KGO) - S\\u00e1ng 10-12, S\\u1edf V\\u0103n h\\u00f3a v\\u00e0 Th\\u1ec3 thao t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang, Li\\u00ean \\u0111o\\u00e0n Taekwondo t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p Li\\u00ean \\u0111o\\u00e0n Taekwondo Vi\\u1ec7t Nam khai m\\u1ea1c k\\u1ef3 thi th\\u0103ng \\u0111\\u1eb3ng Taekwondo t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang n\\u0103m 2023.<\\/h2>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"newscontent\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid\\\">\\u00a0\",\"fulltext\":\"<\\/div>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.baokiengiang.vn\\/uploads\\/images\\/2023\\/12\\/10\\/092857KGO_20231210_TAEKWONDO2.webp\\\" alt=\\\"092857KGO_20231210_TAEKWONDO2\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>V\\u00f5 sinh trong ph\\u1ea7n\\u00a0thi quy\\u1ec1n.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Tham d\\u1ef1 k\\u1ef3 thi th\\u0103ng \\u0111\\u1eb3ng Taekwondo t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang n\\u0103m 2023 c\\u00f3 118 h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn vi\\u00ean, v\\u00f5 sinh c\\u1ee7a 22 c\\u00e2u l\\u1ea1c b\\u1ed9 Taekwondo c\\u00e1c huy\\u1ec7n, th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ecba b\\u00e0n t\\u1ec9nh; thi th\\u0103ng c\\u1ea5p 1, 2 v\\u00e0 3 \\u0111\\u1eb3ng.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>V\\u01b0\\u1ee3t qua k\\u1ef3 thi,\\u00a0h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn vi\\u00ean, v\\u00f5 sinh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u1ea5p b\\u1eb1ng Kukkiwon v\\u00e0 gi\\u1ea5y ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn c\\u1ee7a Li\\u00ean \\u0111o\\u00e0n Taekwondo t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi c\\u1ea5p 1 \\u0111\\u1eb3ng; gi\\u1ea5y ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn c\\u1ee7a Li\\u00ean \\u0111o\\u00e0n Taekwondo Vi\\u1ec7t Nam \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi c\\u1ea5p 2 v\\u00e0 3 \\u0111\\u1eb3ng.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.baokiengiang.vn\\/uploads\\/images\\/2023\\/12\\/10\\/093637KGO_20231210_TAEKWONDO1.webp\\\" alt=\\\"093637KGO_20231210_TAEKWONDO1\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>V\\u00f5 sinh thi song \\u0111\\u1ea5u.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Theo Li\\u00ean \\u0111o\\u00e0n Taekwondo t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang, vi\\u1ec7c t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c\\u00a0k\\u1ef3 thi th\\u0103ng \\u0111\\u1eb3ng nh\\u1eb1m r\\u00e0 so\\u00e1t, \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ed9 chuy\\u00ean m\\u00f4n c\\u1ee7a h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn vi\\u00ean, v\\u00f5 sinh t\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c c\\u00e2u l\\u1ea1c b\\u1ed9 Taekwondo trong to\\u00e0n t\\u1ec9nh. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, t\\u1ea1o \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n cho \\u0111\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 hu\\u1ea5n luy\\u1ec7n vi\\u00ean, h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn vi\\u00ean v\\u00e0\\u00a0v\\u00f5 sinh c\\u00e1c c\\u00e2u l\\u1ea1c b\\u1ed9 Taekwondo trong t\\u1ec9nh c\\u00f3 d\\u1ecbp giao l\\u01b0u, trao \\u0111\\u1ed5i chuy\\u00ean m\\u00f4n, nghi\\u1ec7p v\\u1ee5, \\u0111\\u1ea9y m\\u1ea1nh phong tr\\u00e0o Taekwondo t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang th\\u1eddi gian t\\u1edbi.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Hi\\u1ec7n Ki\\u00ean Giang c\\u00f3 6 hu\\u1ea5n luy\\u1ec7n vi\\u00ean Taekwondo tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ed9 5 \\u0111\\u1eb3ng, 13 hu\\u1ea5n luy\\u1ec7n vi\\u00ean tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ed9 4 \\u0111\\u1eb3ng, 26 h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn vi\\u00ean tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ed9 3 \\u0111\\u1eb3ng...<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Tin v\\u00e0 \\u1ea3nh:<strong>\\u00a0TRUNG HI\\u1ebeU<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2024-01-05 01:06:37\",\"created_by\":\"674\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-01-05 01:23:21\",\"modified_by\":\"674\",\"checked_out\":\"674\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2024-01-05 01:23:17\",\"publish_up\":\"2024-01-05 01:06:37\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",