(123, 12, 1, '', '2024-01-06 05:52:28', 674, 6879, 'bf86d823022adb5d6302b1166b41c77e1b58a5fa', '{\"id\":12,\"asset_id\":\"84\",\"title\":\"Nhi\\u1ec1u quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh quan tr\\u1ecdng v\\u1ec1 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf - x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i n\\u0103m 2024\",\"alias\":\"nhi-u-quy-t-d-nh-quan-tr-ng-v-phat-tri-n-kinh-t-xa-h-i-nam-2024\",\"introtext\":\"<header class=\\\"detail__header\\\"><img src=\\\"images\\/kgphattrioen.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><img src=\\\"images\\/z5008035318071-ac2a711e0bc725b40dc9a761abffdf8f.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/>\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<h2 class=\\\"detail__summary\\\">Kinhtedothi - Ng\\u00e0y 25\\/12, H\\u0110ND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang kh\\u00f3a X, nhi\\u1ec7m k\\u1ef3 2021-2026 t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c k\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp th\\u1ee9 20 \\u0111\\u1ec3 xem xem x\\u00e9t, \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 t\\u00ecnh h\\u00ecnh th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n ngh\\u1ecb quy\\u1ebft c\\u1ee7a H\\u0110ND t\\u1ec9nh v\\u1ec1 nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf- x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i n\\u0103m 2023 v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ec1 ra nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n n\\u0103m 2024.<\\/h2>\\r\\n<h2 class=\\\"detail__summary\\\">Theo \\u0111\\u00f3, t\\u1ea1i K\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp n\\u00e0y, H\\u0110ND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang xem x\\u00e9t, quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh 4 n\\u1ed9i dung quan tr\\u1ecdng g\\u1ed3m: Xem x\\u00e9t, \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 t\\u00ecnh h\\u00ecnh th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n ngh\\u1ecb quy\\u1ebft c\\u1ee7a H\\u0110ND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang v\\u1ec1 nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n KT - XH n\\u0103m 2023 v\\u00e0 k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf - x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i n\\u0103m 2024; C\\u00e1c b\\u00e1o c\\u00e1o c\\u1ee7a Th\\u01b0\\u1eddng tr\\u1ef1c H\\u0110ND, c\\u00e1c ban H\\u0110ND, UBND, c\\u00e1c c\\u01a1 quan t\\u01b0 ph\\u00e1p t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang\\u00a0n\\u0103m 2023 v\\u00e0 nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 n\\u0103m 2024.<\\/h2>\\r\\n<\\/header>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"detail__content-wrap\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"detail__content\\\">\\r\\n<figure class=\\\"image-wrap align-center-image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/static.kinhtedothi.vn\\/w960\\/images\\/upload\\/2023\\/12\\/25\\/z5008035318071-ac2a711e0bc725b40dc9a761abffdf8f.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"To&amp;agrave;n c\\u1ea3nh k\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp th\\u1ee9 20 H\\u0110ND kh&amp;oacute;a X nhi\\u1ec7m k\\u1ef3 2021-2026. (\\u1ea2nh H\\u1eefu Tu\\u1ea5n)\\\" data-original=\\\"https:\\/\\/static.kinhtedothi.vn\\/images\\/upload\\/\\/2023\\/12\\/25\\/z5008035318071-ac2a711e0bc725b40dc9a761abffdf8f.jpg\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<figcaption class=\\\"image-caption\\\">To\\u00e0n c\\u1ea3nh k\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp th\\u1ee9 20 H\\u0110ND kh\\u00f3a X nhi\\u1ec7m k\\u1ef3 2021-2026. (\\u1ea2nh H\\u1eefu Tu\\u1ea5n)<\\/figcaption>\\r\\n<\\/figure>\\r\\n<p>\\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, nghe \\u1ee6y ban M\\u1eb7t tr\\u1eadn T\\u1ed5 qu\\u1ed1c Vi\\u1ec7t Nam t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang\\u00a0th\\u00f4ng b\\u00e1o t\\u00ecnh h\\u00ecnh ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u1ee7a M\\u1eb7t tr\\u1eadn tham gia x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng ch\\u00ednh quy\\u1ec1n n\\u0103m 2023, nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 n\\u0103m 2024; b\\u00e1o c\\u00e1o gi\\u00e1m s\\u00e1t k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 gi\\u1ea3i quy\\u1ebft ki\\u1ebfn ngh\\u1ecb c\\u1ee7a c\\u1eed tri tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0 sau K\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp th\\u01b0\\u1eddng l\\u1ec7 gi\\u1eefa n\\u0103m 2023. Xem x\\u00e9t c\\u00e1c t\\u1edd tr\\u00ecnh c\\u1ee7a Th\\u01b0\\u1eddng tr\\u1ef1c H\\u0110ND, UBND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang; gi\\u1ea3i tr\\u00ecnh, ch\\u1ea5t v\\u1ea5n v\\u00e0 tr\\u1ea3 l\\u1eddi ch\\u1ea5t v\\u1ea5n; th\\u00f4ng qua c\\u00e1c ngh\\u1ecb quy\\u1ebft c\\u1ee7a H\\u0110ND tr\\u00ecnh K\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>N\\u0103m 2023, t\\u00ecnh h\\u00ecnh KT - XH n\\u0103m 2023 c\\u1ee7a t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kh\\u00e1; c\\u00f3 23\\/24 ch\\u1ec9 ti\\u00eau \\u0111\\u1ea1t v\\u00e0 v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch, c\\u00f2n l\\u1ea1i 1 ch\\u1ec9 ti\\u00eau \\u0111\\u1ea1t tr\\u00ean 90% k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch. T\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 t\\u0103ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng kinh t\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ea1t 6,79%. Thu ng\\u00e2n s\\u00e1ch v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t ch\\u1ec9 ti\\u00eau \\u0111\\u1ec1 ra.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>T\\u1ed5ng kh\\u00e1ch du l\\u1ecbch trong n\\u0103m \\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u00f3n tr\\u00ean 8,5 tri\\u1ec7u l\\u01b0\\u1ee3t kh\\u00e1ch, t\\u0103ng 15,6% (kh\\u00e1ch qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf, t\\u0103ng 177%), t\\u1ed5ng doanh thu t\\u0103ng 65% so c\\u00f9ng k\\u1ef3. T\\u1ed5ng thu ng\\u00e2n s\\u00e1ch h\\u01a1n 15.120 t\\u1ef7 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng, v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t 24% k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch, t\\u0103ng 26,8% so c\\u00f9ng k\\u1ef3.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00d4ng Mai V\\u0103n Hu\\u1ef3nh, Ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch H\\u0110ND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang cho bi\\u1ebft, t\\u1ea1i K\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp n\\u00e0y, H\\u0110ND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang\\u00a0xem x\\u00e9t, cho \\u00fd ki\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi 48 n\\u1ed9i dung b\\u00e1o c\\u00e1o, t\\u1edd tr\\u00ecnh, d\\u1ef1 th\\u1ea3o ngh\\u1ecb quy\\u1ebft; c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u1ed9i dung quan tr\\u1ecdng t\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ebfn s\\u1ef1 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n KT - XH, qu\\u1ed1c ph\\u00f2ng, an ninh, \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o an sinh x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, \\u0111\\u1ec1 ngh\\u1ecb c\\u00e1c v\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u1ea1i bi\\u1ec3u ph\\u00e1t huy d\\u00e2n ch\\u1ee7, n\\u00eau cao tinh th\\u1ea7n tr\\u00e1ch nhi\\u1ec7m, t\\u00edch c\\u1ef1c tham gia th\\u1ea3o lu\\u1eadn, \\u0111\\u00f3ng g\\u00f3p nhi\\u1ec1u \\u00fd ki\\u1ebfn ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u00e1c n\\u1ed9i dung tr\\u00ecnh K\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"11\",\"created\":\"2024-01-05 01:09:19\",\"created_by\":\"674\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-01-06 05:52:28\",\"modified_by\":\"674\",\"checked_out\":\"674\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2024-01-06 05:52:16\",\"publish_up\":\"2024-01-05 01:09:19\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":6,\"ordering\":\"1\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"1\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"1\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(124, 13, 1, '', '2024-01-06 05:52:51', 674, 9538, 'c162bb2d7767ec9585edbd7ba6d8a7d86a5ee90d', '{\"id\":13,\"asset_id\":\"85\",\"title\":\"Ki\\u00ean Giang ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i, \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf - x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i\",\"alias\":\"kien-giang-ph-c-h-i-n-d-nh-va-phat-tri-n-kinh-t-xa-h-i\",\"introtext\":\"<p><img src=\\\"images\\/phatbieu.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><img src=\\\"images\\/1mvhuynh-6223.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p>(PLVN) -\\u00a0 N\\u0103m 2023, t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang c\\u00f3 quy m\\u00f4 t\\u1ed5ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ecba b\\u00e0n (GRDP) \\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ea1t 73.377 t\\u1ef7 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng, v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t 0,68% k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch, t\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 t\\u0103ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng 6,79%.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"article__body cms-body \\\">\\r\\n<p>Ng\\u00e0y 25\\/12, H\\u0110ND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang kho\\u00e1 X, nhi\\u1ec7m k\\u1ef3 2021 - 2026, khai m\\u1ea1c k\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp 20 (k\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp cu\\u1ed1i n\\u0103m 2023) t\\u1ed5ng k\\u1ebft t\\u00ecnh h\\u00ecnh ngh\\u1ecb quy\\u1ebft c\\u1ee7a H\\u0110ND t\\u1ec9nh v\\u1ec1 nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf - x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i n\\u0103m 2023 v\\u00e0 xem x\\u00e9t gi\\u1ea3i quy\\u1ebft m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 n\\u1ed9i dung thu\\u1ed9c th\\u1ea7m quy\\u1ec1n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<table class=\\\"picture\\\">\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td class=\\\"pic\\\"><img class=\\\"cms-photo lazyloaded\\\" title=\\\"\\u00d4ng Mai V\\u0103n Hu\\u1ef3nh - Ph\\u00f3 b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 T\\u1ec9nh u\\u1ef7 Ki\\u00ean Giang, Ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch H\\u0110ND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang - ph\\u00e1t bi\\u1ec3u khai m\\u1ea1c k\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp 20 (k\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp cu\\u1ed1i n\\u0103m) c\\u1ee7a H\\u0110ND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang kho\\u00e1 X, nhi\\u1ec7m k\\u1ef3 2021-2026 (\\u1ea2nh: Kh\\u00e1nh Thu\\u1ef3)\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me\\/w840\\/Uploaded\\/2023\\/zshvwyvobvhvim\\/2023_12_25\\/1mvhuynh-6223.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\u00d4ng Mai V\\u0103n Hu\\u1ef3nh - Ph\\u00f3 b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 T\\u1ec9nh u\\u1ef7 Ki\\u00ean Giang, Ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch H\\u0110ND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang - ph\\u00e1t bi\\u1ec3u khai m\\u1ea1c k\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp 20 (k\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp cu\\u1ed1i n\\u0103m) c\\u1ee7a H\\u0110ND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang kho\\u00e1 X, nhi\\u1ec7m k\\u1ef3 2021-2026 (\\u1ea2nh: Kh\\u00e1nh Thu\\u1ef3)\\\" width=\\\"840\\\" height=\\\"560\\\" data-height=\\\"1707\\\" data-image-id=\\\"947668\\\" data-src=\\\"https:\\/\\/photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me\\/w840\\/Uploaded\\/2023\\/zshvwyvobvhvim\\/2023_12_25\\/1mvhuynh-6223.jpg\\\" data-width=\\\"2560\\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td class=\\\"caption\\\">\\r\\n<p>\\u00d4ng Mai V\\u0103n Hu\\u1ef3nh - Ph\\u00f3 b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 T\\u1ec9nh u\\u1ef7 Ki\\u00ean Giang, Ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch H\\u0110ND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang - ph\\u00e1t bi\\u1ec3u khai m\\u1ea1c k\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp 20 (k\\u1ef3 h\\u1ecdp cu\\u1ed1i n\\u0103m) c\\u1ee7a H\\u0110ND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang kho\\u00e1 X, nhi\\u1ec7m k\\u1ef3 2021-2026 (\\u1ea2nh: Kh\\u00e1nh Thu\\u1ef3)<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<p>\\u00d4ng Nguy\\u1ec5n Thanh Nh\\u00e0n - Ph\\u00f3 Ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch UBND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang - cho bi\\u1ebft: N\\u0103m 2023, t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang c\\u00f3 quy m\\u00f4 t\\u1ed5ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ecba b\\u00e0n t\\u1ec9nh (GRDP) \\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ea1t 73.377 t\\u1ef7 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng, v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t 0,68% k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch, t\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 t\\u0103ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng 6,79% (k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch 6,5%).<\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ads_middle\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p>N\\u00f4ng - l\\u00e2m - th\\u1ee7y s\\u1ea3n \\u1edf \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u0103ng 2,96%; c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p - x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng, t\\u0103ng 8,36%; th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i - d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5, t\\u0103ng 10,02%; thu\\u1ebf s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m tr\\u1eeb tr\\u1ee3 c\\u1ea5p s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m, t\\u0103ng 5,95%; c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p - x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng, chi\\u1ebfm 20,53%<em>;<\\/em>\\u00a0d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 chi\\u1ebfm 37,53% v\\u00e0 thu\\u1ebf nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u, thu\\u1ebf s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m tr\\u1eeb tr\\u1ee3 c\\u1ea5p s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m chi\\u1ebfm 4,92%<em>.<\\/em>\\u00a0GRDP b\\u00ecnh qu\\u00e2n \\u0111\\u1ea7u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u1edf \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ea1t 73,74 tri\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u1ed3ng, t\\u0103ng 3,85% k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u0110\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t, n\\u0103m 2023, t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang \\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u00f3n tr\\u00ean 8,5 tri\\u1ec7u l\\u01b0\\u1ee3t kh\\u00e1ch, v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t 2,8% k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch, t\\u0103ng 15% so c\\u00f9ng k\\u1ef3. Ri\\u00eang kh\\u00e1ch du l\\u1ecbch qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ea1t 573.000 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3t, v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t 63,8% k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch, t\\u1ed5ng doanh thu du l\\u1ecbch g\\u1ea7n 17.500 t\\u1ef7 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ads_middle\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<table class=\\\"picture\\\">\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td class=\\\"pic\\\"><img class=\\\"cms-photo lazyloaded\\\" title=\\\"\\u00d4ng Nguy\\u1ec5n Thanh Nh\\u00e0n - Ph\\u00f3 Ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch UBND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang - cho bi\\u1ebft n\\u0103m 2023, Ki\\u00ean Giang ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd. (\\u1ea2nh: Kh\\u00e1nh Thu\\u1ef3)\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me\\/w840\\/Uploaded\\/2023\\/zshvwyvobvhvim\\/2023_12_25\\/1ngthanhnhan-3602.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\u00d4ng Nguy\\u1ec5n Thanh Nh\\u00e0n - Ph\\u00f3 Ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch UBND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang - cho bi\\u1ebft n\\u0103m 2023, Ki\\u00ean Giang ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd. (\\u1ea2nh: Kh\\u00e1nh Thu\\u1ef3)\\\" width=\\\"840\\\" height=\\\"647\\\" data-height=\\\"987\\\" data-image-id=\\\"947669\\\" data-src=\\\"https:\\/\\/photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me\\/w840\\/Uploaded\\/2023\\/zshvwyvobvhvim\\/2023_12_25\\/1ngthanhnhan-3602.jpg\\\" data-width=\\\"1280\\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td class=\\\"caption\\\">\\r\\n<p>\\u00d4ng Nguy\\u1ec5n Thanh Nh\\u00e0n - Ph\\u00f3 Ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch UBND t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang - cho bi\\u1ebft n\\u0103m 2023, Ki\\u00ean Giang ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd. (\\u1ea2nh: Kh\\u00e1nh Thu\\u1ef3)<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<p>\\u00d4ng Nh\\u00e0n cho bi\\u1ebft th\\u00eam: Kinh t\\u1ebf tuy c\\u00f3 ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i v\\u00e0 t\\u0103ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u00e1; c\\u01a1 c\\u1ea5u kinh t\\u1ebf chuy\\u1ec3n d\\u1ecbch \\u0111\\u00fang h\\u01b0\\u1edbng, nh\\u01b0ng c\\u00f2n ch\\u1eadm. Do \\u0111\\u00f3, \\u0111\\u1ec3 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i trong n\\u0103m 2024, \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c t\\u1eadp trung th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n c\\u00e1c ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch g\\u00f3p ph\\u1ea7n ki\\u1ec3m so\\u00e1t l\\u1ea1m ph\\u00e1t, \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh n\\u1ec1n kinh t\\u1ebf; \\u0111\\u1ea9y m\\u1ea1nh gi\\u1ea3i ng\\u00e2n v\\u1ed1n \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 c\\u00f4ng, t\\u1ea1o n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng cho ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n nhanh v\\u00e0 b\\u1ec1n v\\u1eefng. B\\u00ean c\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u00f3, t\\u1ec9nh Ki\\u00ean Giang th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ed3ng b\\u1ed9, hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 c\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c c\\u1ea3i c\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0nh ch\\u00ednh, c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng kinh doanh. T\\u1ea1o \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n c\\u00e1c th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n kinh t\\u1ebf, n\\u00e2ng cao n\\u0103ng l\\u1ef1c c\\u1ea1nh tranh tr\\