(154, 7, 1, '', '2024-01-06 08:21:11', 674, 4168, 'bd210a8c40ddcb5e43b9fed7be68c43817009ec1', '{\"id\":7,\"asset_id\":\"79\",\"title\":\"KG \\u0111o\\u1ea1t 1 huy ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng b\\u1ea1c, gi\\u1ea3i c\\u1eed t\\u1ea1 v\\u00f4 \\u0111\\u1ecbch qu\\u1ed1c gia 2023\",\"alias\":\"kien-giang-do-t-1-huy-chuong-b-c-2-huy-chuong-d-ng-gi-i-c-t-vo-d-ch-qu-c-gia-2023\",\"introtext\":\"<p><img src=\\\"images\\/t\\u1ea3i xu\\u1ed1ng.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"616\\\" height=\\\"437\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<h2 class=\\\"title-italic\\\">(KGO) - Thi \\u0111\\u1ea5u \\u0111\\u1ea7y c\\u1ed1 g\\u1eafng, hai v\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng vi\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a Ki\\u00ean Giang \\u0111o\\u1ea1t 3 huy ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ea3i c\\u1eed t\\u1ea1 v\\u00f4 \\u0111\\u1ecbch qu\\u1ed1c gia 2023.<\\/h2>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"newscontent\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid\\\">\\u00a0<img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.baokiengiang.vn\\/uploads\\/images\\/2023\\/12\\/20\\/141653KGO_20231220_CUTA2.webp\\\" alt=\\\"141653KGO_20231220_CUTA2\\\" \\/><\\/div>\\r\\n<p><em>H\\u00ecnh Loan Anh (b\\u00eca ph\\u1ea3i) \\u0111o\\u1ea1t\\u00a02 huy ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng t\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ea3i c\\u1eed t\\u1ea1\\u00a0v\\u00f4 \\u0111\\u1ecbch qu\\u1ed1c gia n\\u0103m 2023.<\\/em>\\u00a0\\u1ea2nh<strong>: QU\\u1ed0C PHI.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Ng\\u00e0y 20-12, Ph\\u00f3 Gi\\u00e1m \\u0111\\u1ed1c Trung t\\u00e2m hu\\u1ea5n luy\\u1ec7n v\\u00e0 thi \\u0111\\u1ea5u th\\u1ec3 thao Ki\\u00ean Giang Nguy\\u1ec5n Qu\\u1ed1c Phi cho bi\\u1ebft, gi\\u1ea3i c\\u1eed t\\u1ea1 v\\u00f4 \\u0111\\u1ecbch qu\\u1ed1c gia 2023 di\\u1ec5n ra t\\u1ea1i TP H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh, thu h\\u00fat tr\\u00ean 170 l\\u01b0\\u0323c s\\u0129 nam, n\\u1eef m\\u1ea1nh nh\\u1ea5t t\\u01b0\\u0300 27 \\u0111\\u01a1n vi\\u0323 trong ca\\u0309 n\\u01b0\\u01a1\\u0301c tham d\\u1ef1.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u0110\\u00e2y c\\u0169ng l\\u00e0 gi\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1ea5u \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u1eed t\